metadata.name: STRONG HAIR : 001 : ፩
metadata.description:
Afar hairstyle, 1/1.

Looping 360° motion portrait from the Yatreda series “STRONG HAIR : ጠንካራ ፀጉር” which merges the diversity and power of African hair with the blockchain. This collection features 100 unique hairstyles from all across Ethiopia.

Format: 2880 x 2160 video
  Behind the Scenes: https://youtu.be/12Km5-ZSjBA
